item.title: Meet Tzipora Desmoines, the Eternal Teen-ager and Princess of the Earth
item.description: Archived from the original article here ðŸŒ¸ Archived Post This article predates the project, and should be considered non-canon. This is Tzipora. She goes by two names – Tzipora, her birth name, and Zelda, a name she mistakenly thought sounded less Jewish. She lives in Lola in the Vekllei city-state. As an immigrant, she struggles with school but holds her own on in track and field, an inversion of her otherwise quiet and bookish nature.
